Lagi pula, wajahmu masih agak merah.

44
00:04:38.128 --> 00:04:40.128
Apa?

45
00:04:40.128 --> 00:04:43.728
Kalau begitu, kau tetap tidur saja hari ini, ya.

46
00:04:43.728 --> 00:04:45.128
Oke.

47
