228
00:14:54.395 --> 00:14:56.895
Lihat? Panah lain muncul.

229
00:14:59.095 --> 00:15:02.195
-Benar katamu! -Wow!

230
00:15:02.195 --> 00:15:03.795
Artinya...

231
00:15:05.195 --> 00:15:09.295
Panah tidak menunjuk pintu masuk,

232
00:15:09.295 --> 00:15:13.495
tapi ke sini, ke ruangan ini.

233
00:15:13.495 --> 00:15:14.795
Ya...

234
00:15:17.595 --> 00:15:19.895
Maria, apa kau di dalam?

